<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>The Bachelorette's Carlin Sterritt has gained an army of female fans by showing his soft and caring side since his split with Angie Kent. </p>

<p>But on Sunday, the personal trainer gave fans more than they bargained for when he stripped down to just a pair of snug-fitting sports shorts.</p>

<p>Taking to Instagram, Carlin let imaginations run wild as he posed in front of the mirror showing off his toned and tanned physique.</p>

<p>Hello! The Bachelorette's Carlin Sterritt, 32, (pictured) left little to the imagination while going shirtless in snug-fitting shorts for a raunchy mirror selfie on Sunday</p>

<p>Carlin wore just a pair of grey sleep shorts which hugged his muscular frame. </p>

<p>'Ok, that's enough sun for a while,' Carlin captioned the post. </p>

<p>Earlier in the day, the reality TV star had been soaking up the sun alongside his pals with him clearly enjoying himself. </p>

<p>It comes after Carlin showed himself getting biblical-inspired tattoos on his Instagram Stories earlier this week. </p>

<p>Feeling hot, hot, hot: Earlier in the day, the reality TV star had been soaking up the sun alongside his pals with him clearly enjoying himself</p>

<p>Keeping the faith: Carlin got two biblical tattoos last Monday, after his split from Angie Kent in July </p>

<p>On Monday, Carlin had a quill with a psalm verse etched onto one forearm, as well as a religious take on Leonardo da Vinci's Vitruvian Man on one bicep. </p>

<p>'If I rise on the wings on the dawn,' the verse surrounding the quill read.</p>

<p>This month, Angie, 30, revealed on radio that she and Carlin, who met on the 2019 season of The Bachelorette, called it quits because their 'values didn't align'.  </p>

<p>Religious: On Instagram Stories, the fitness trainer showed off a quill with a psalm verse on one forearm. The verse read: 'If I rise on the wings of the dawn' </p>

<p>'Chemistry doesn't always equal compatibly,' she said on The Kyle and Jackie O Show.   </p>

<p>'Our values were different. I'm a little more spiritual, a little bit more carefree and wild. He's a Christian boy... we're just different.' </p>

<p>The blonde beauty also told House Of Wellness that she has been seeking professional help with the heartbreaking split, dealing with feelings as they arise.</p>

<p>'I am navigating it all and dealing with the feelings and thoughts as they arise... and have an amazing therapist who is helping,' she told the website.</p>

<p>Intricate: Carlin also had a religious take on Leonardo da Vinci's Vitruvian Man etched on one bicep. It represents what is thought to be the divine connection between the human form and the universe  </p>

<p>Meanwhile, Carlin told Instagram fans in July that their breakup had 'taken a toll' on him, while discussing his battle with anxiety.</p>

<p>The fitness trainer said: 'Everybody has actually been really kind. I had so much fear and anxiety about coming out about our breakup publicly.  </p>

<p>'It was actually quite debilitating each day when I was holding on to that truth. Yes we have come up with the decision [to split] recently, but I've just been so scared.' </p>

<p>Not compatible: Angie revealed on The Kyle and Jackie O Show in September that she and Carlin called it quits because their 'values didn't align' </p>
